node.text: I have been very selective lately of what weed brands I’ve been smoking. Over the course of this last year, my tolerance has changed drastically and as well as my strain preferences. Some of my usual favorites weren’t helping me relax like they used to. I was introduced to @AutumnBrands and I’m in love! They're an incredible Santa Barbara based, highly sustainable, 50% women - owned business and I love the quality of their products. Some of their strains help tremendously with my anxiety and insomnia which is oftentimes trial and error for me. I would highly recommend this lovely brand. ♥️✨ #AutumnBrands #InhaleExhaleSmile #ad

node.text: My mom is the bravest and most badass person I know. She’s traveled to and from South Korea and has been protesting the horrific dog meat trade that is somehow still going down in parts of our world. I urge you to visit www.stopdogmeat.com and watch the new undercover footage showing what unspeakable conditions these poor dogs have to endure. I know it’s a tough watch but as my mom would say, they don’t need your tears, they need your help! See how you can help but visiting the site or checking out the link in @kim.basinger ‘s bio!
